narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned about the current research done in the chemical biology field. It helped me relate my research to other projects going on

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The strengths are definitely the speakers invited. I really enjoyed it. I would not mind however have more seminars

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: It will be good if we can have some of the Chemical Biology seminars on West Campus. I don't think any of the talks were held on West Campus this semester and the broadcast sometimes had issues.
Yes definitely it is a good way to find out what is being researched out there
